# Phase 4 Mobile Development Rules (Mandatory)

Phase 2 complete and frozen. Phase 4 = **React Native only** (`mobile-rn/`). Sequence: [04-development-sequence.md](../../docs/vsp/phase4/04-development-sequence.md)

## Backend freeze (STRICT)

Do NOT modify backend unless approved production bug. Backend bug → **STOP**, report root cause / files / fix. **No mobile workarounds.**

## Inspect before modifying telephony

Before changing SIP registration, call controller, push, auth, QR provisioning, or call state — **read existing code first**. Decide if change is necessary.

| Area | Start here |
|------|------------|
| SIP registration | `sip/service.ts`, `calling/TelnyxCallingProvider.tsx` |
| Call controller | `calling/callingController.ts` |
| Push | `notifications/PushNotificationProvider.tsx` |
| Auth | `store/authStore.ts`, `auth/authService.ts` |
| QR provisioning | `auth/provisionService.ts`, `screens/QrLoginScreen.tsx` |
| Call state | `store/callingStore.ts`, `calling/CallOverlay.tsx` |

**Extend — do not replace** working modules.

## Do not rewrite

No rewrites for style/architecture preference. Incremental improvements only. Preserve API contracts and public interfaces unless explicitly approved.

## Telephony

Production-approved flows. Reuse `calling/*`, `sip/*`, notifications. Verify `docs/telnyx/` before signaling/media changes. UI must not alter call behavior.

## UI/UX & performance

Premium enterprise UI (`mobile-rn/docs/DESIGN.md`). 60 FPS, FlashList, memoization, lazy loading. One feature production-ready before the next.

## Completion

`npm run test:mobile` · no backend changes · mandatory handoff report.

Full rules: `docs/vsp/phase4/03-mobile-development-rules.md`
